      <guid>https://theweeklychallenge.org/blog/what-is-middleware/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h4 id=&#34;disclaimer-image-is-generated-using-chatgpt&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DISCLAIMER:&lt;/strong&gt; Image is generated using &lt;code&gt;ChatGPT&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In the early &lt;code&gt;2000s&lt;/code&gt;, I was exposed to middleware, but I have never used it on a work project in my career.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;When I was introduced to middleware while building a &lt;a href=&#34;https://metacpan.org/pod/Dancer2&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dancer2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; application and learned about &lt;a href=&#34;https://metacpan.org/pod/Plack&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Plack&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, I saw it used in the real world for the first time through the &lt;a href=&#34;https://metacpan.org/pod/Plack::Middleware&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Plack::Middleware&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; module.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Since then, &lt;code&gt;Plack&lt;/code&gt; has been my top choice; for example, my personal website, &lt;a href=&#34;https://manwar.org&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;https://manwar.org&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, is a &lt;code&gt;Dancer2&lt;/code&gt; application and is built with the help of &lt;code&gt;Plack&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
